116
00:09:45,043 --> 00:09:46,295
Tu le connaissais.

117
00:09:46,628 --> 00:09:48,255
- Qui?
- Steadman.

118
00:09:48,297 --> 00:09:49,006
Non.

119
00:09:49,131 --> 00:09:50,894
